content.text: I'll read each image file and describe what products they show.

Here's a description of each product image:

## 1. fleje de cobre.png
**Product:** Copper straps/strips (Flejes de Cobre)
**Quality Assessment:** Good - Clean isometric 3D rendering showing a grid pattern of copper straps with clear visibility. The white background and professional render make it suitable for product pages. Shows the flexibility and form of the material well.

## 2. Flejes-de-Cobre-1.jpg
**Product:** Copper strips/coils in various forms
**Quality Assessment:** Excellent - Professional product photography showing copper straps both coiled and flat. Multiple angles visible with good lighting that highlights the copper's reflective properties. Very suitable for a product page - shows versatility of the product.

## 3. Flejes-de-Cobre-3.jpg
**Product:** Copper strap on industrial rod/pipe
**Quality Assessment:** Good - Real-world application photo showing a copper strap wrapped around what appears to be a grounding rod or industrial pipe. Shows practical use case. Slightly blurred background adds focus to the product. Good for demonstrating installation context.

## 4. Cable-desnudo-de-Cobre-1.jpg
**Product:** Bare copper cable/wire (Cable desnudo de Cobre)
**Quality Assessment:** Excellent - Clean, professional product shot of a coil of bare copper wire with white background. Shows the product clearly from a good angle. Appropriate for e-commerce product pages with good detail visibility.

## 5. barra toma tierra 2.webp
**Product:** Copper grounding rod/bar (Barra de toma tierra)
**Quality Assessment:** Good - Shows solid copper rods/bars with pointed tips used for grounding applications. Professional 3D render with white background. Clear view of the product's form and pointed design. Suitable for product pages.

## 6. Barra Toma Tierra Copperweld.png
**Product:** Grounding rod/bar (Barra de toma tierra Copperweld brand)
**Quality Assessment:** Good - Professional product photograph of copper-clad steel grounding rods with pointed tips. Angled view shows the product detail well. Slightly gray background. Suitable for product listings, though a pure white background might be more consistent with the others.

**Summary:** All images are of high enough quality for product pages. Images 2 and 4 are the strongest (professional photography with clean backgrounds). These appear to be components for grounding systems and electrical protection - core products for GelChile's business.
